The paper discusses the issue of data integrity in AI systems, which is a common topic in the database (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) communities. The paper also proposes a solution to the problem of data integrity by guaranteeing it throughout the enterprise, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and potentially cryptography (cs.CR) techniques. Finally, the paper mentions the issue of spending too much time cleaning data, which is a common problem in machine learning (cs.LG) research.
